00:37:57.350 --> 00:38:08.494
You could literally hear them coming, and they could sense your body heat, your motion, and everything.

00:38:08.495 --> 00:38:22.394
So, you couldn't hide from them. The only way I saw that the Christians could hide from them was digging into the side of the hills. The drones were looking for smoke or gunshots.

00:38:22.395 --> 00:38:36.533
So the Christians couldn't shoot for food—rabbits or deer or anything that made noise—because the drones in the sky could hear the noises.

00:38:36.534 --> 00:38:43.206
They were alerted and would swarm to that area and see who did it.

00:38:43.207 --> 00:38:48.611
If you had the chip, it would report back and they would just go on about their business.

00:38:48.612 --> 00:38:56.256
But if you didn't have the chip, they would call for the authorities, who would come and stay there until they arrived.

00:38:56.257 --> 00:39:02.065
You would run, but you couldn't get away. You couldn't get away from them because they were up like a helicopter.

00:39:02.066 --> 00:39:07.056
They were flying over, and once they found you, you were done.

00:39:07.057 --> 00:39:16.185
They would come and either you took the chip or you took the mark, or they cut your head off.

00:39:16.186 --> 00:39:30.459
These Christians were all on the side of mountains—people that were still fighting to live and survive, who were not living for Jesus when they were on the earth, but they knew the truth.

00:39:30.460 --> 00:39:39.131
They knew. The children were the hardest part for me, those born during the Tribulation.

00:39:39.132 --> 00:39:56.879
I know there's a Bible verse that says, 'Woe to those that give suck in those days.'I believe that verse is talking about the Tribulation, but all I know is that the kids were taking it really hard.

00:39:56.880 --> 00:40:00.976
They were going inside, and the smoke was coming out of these caves.

00:40:00.977 --> 00:40:09.683
