00:40:09.684 --> 00:40:18.740
The drones would fly throughout the earth, and they sounded like swarms of bees beyond anything. It was incredibly loud.

00:40:18.741 --> 00:40:24.027
Swarms of bees were everywhere, and you knew when they were coming because you could hear them from a distance.

00:40:24.028 --> 00:40:36.360
Everybody would scramble, trying to get into their safe zone as fast as they could to try to hide themselves. They were made to worship on Fridays.

00:40:36.361 --> 00:40:51.279
