00:48:40.135 --> 00:48:47.443
It's like—and I don't want to add any words that he didn't say, but that's what he showed me.

00:48:47.444 --> 00:48:55.643
And then he started—I look over at him, I'm looking over, and I look at his eyes and they're welled up with tears.

00:48:55.644 --> 00:49:20.525
He said, 'Do you see China?'And I said, 'Yeah.'He said, 'They, a lot of them, died for my gospel.'"The gospel cost them something, Brandon."He looked at him and was so filled with joy at the sacrifice they gave for the gospel.

00:49:20.526 --> 00:49:32.056
What I saw when I was looking over were these gold streams. They were like gold streets, but they weren't, because I knew each one of those lights represented a soul.

