00:53:31.359 --> 00:53:45.358
this massive wave is coming upon the earth, and behind the wave were these angels, and they were all like soldiers on these chariots of fire.

00:53:45.359 --> 00:53:48.403
There were these chariots, and they were golden looking fire.

