00:55:59.982 --> 00:56:11.279
And they had money and they were taking this stuff—which I don't know if it was money or not, I believe it was—and they were pouring it out on the earth.

00:56:11.280 --> 00:56:24.404
They were pouring this out on the earth, and then there were people in these silos, and there were bicycles and things like that that people in foreign countries needed.

