00:57:04.076 --> 00:57:20.772
It was too holy; I can't tell you. But I see all this going on in heaven, and Jesus looked at me and he said, "You need to tell my people I'm coming.

00:57:20.773 --> 00:57:36.253
Tell my people I'm coming."I looked at him like, "Wow. Well, we know."But he was urgent in his eyes: "No, you don't know.

00:57:36.255 --> 00:57:49.144
Tell my people I'm coming."And folks, this was in 2014. Now we're in 2021.

00:57:49.145 --> 00:58:03.608
