01:04:36.354 --> 01:04:39.335
I'm going with Jesus in the rapture. I'm going to believe that.

01:04:39.336 --> 01:04:51.055
And if we're wrong in this scripture and something happens and we're here, you'd better seek me out to tell you what to do next because I'm telling you what's coming, and you're in trouble if you're still here.

01:04:51.056 --> 01:04:55.559
There is some bad stuff fixing to happen to the folks that get left.

01:04:55.560 --> 01:05:00.905
I have seen it. And you may say, "Well, I think you're crazy."Well, that's okay.

01:05:00.906 --> 01:05:09.436
I pray for you, and Jesus loves you, and Jesus cares for you, and he has a plan for your life.

01:05:09.437 --> 01:05:20.892
I'm here to tell you that Jesus loves you and he has a plan for you, and it's not bad; it's to do good for you.

01:05:20.893 --> 01:05:28.821
He wants all your loved ones saved. He wants everybody to not miss the rapture. He wants everybody to have eternal life.

01:05:28.822 --> 01:05:35.168
John 3:16, for God so loved the world that he gave his one and only begotten Son.

01:05:35.169 --> 01:05:42.084
Just remember that. So I pray for you, and that's what I have today.

01:05:42.085 --> 01:05:52.578
The Lord has told me several times to put this out there and to tell people that he's coming.

01:05:52.579 --> 01:06:04.310
And I've been hesitant, probably because of persecution, because of what I'm talking about. But I'm over that. I know the time is coming.

01:06:04.311 --> 01:06:31.677
When they started talking about aliens, just like what he told me when I was standing at the gates of heaven with him, I told my kids, "You'd better understand Jesus is coming, folks; you need to know."One other thing that was really neat: there's a Starbucks coming into our town where I'm at.

01:06:31.678 --> 01:07:02.326
For a long time, whenever I saw it during the tribulation, the Starbucks—and at the time in 2014, it was a barbecue house where they made barbecue—and I never really said it to anybody, but I always said to my kids, "There'll be a Starbucks there during the tribulation right before Jesus comes back."Starbucks is a coffee place; everybody probably knows that.

01:07:02.327 --> 01:07:11.584
If you're in another part of the world watching this, you may not, but it's a coffee shop.

01:07:11.585 --> 01:07:20.292
I told everybody when Jesus comes back, there's going to be a Starbucks there on the corner.

01:07:20.293 --> 01:07:32.118
It was a barbecue house, then it became a Taco Bueno, and then they closed down during the COVID virus thing.

01:07:32.119 --> 01:07:37.617
A couple of weeks ago, about a month or two ago, they bulldozed the building down.

01:07:37.618 --> 01:07:45.686
I said, 'Wow.'I must have missed that; I saw a Starbucks there.

01:07:45.687 --> 01:07:54.624
All of a sudden, they started building a new building there these last couple of weeks, and there's another store next to it.

01:07:54.625 --> 01:08:20.748
I went through the drive-thru and asked, 'Hey, what are they building right there?'The guy said, 'Oh, they're going to build a brand new Starbucks right there.'The buildings that I saw in the Tribulation that didn't exist when I was living in 2014 are being built right now in 2021.

01:08:20.749 --> 01:08:26.858
What I'm trying to tell you is it was a really cool 'awe'moment for me.

01:08:26.859 --> 01:08:31.956
I just want to tell you Jesus loves you and you need to get right.

01:08:31.957 --> 01:08:44.200
If you're living in a compromising lifestyle and a sinful state, and you know Jesus but you've fallen away, today's your day to come back to Him.

01:08:44.201 --> 01:08:51.353
I want to pray for you. Father, I thank You right now for whoever is watching on this side of the camera.

01:08:51.354 --> 01:09:08.706
I lift them up before You and thank You that they become on-fire, born-again Christians who are radically saved and have an urgency regarding the time we're living in.

01:09:08.707 --> 01:09:26.465
Father, I thank You that You stir in their spirits right now and that they find You in a new way—a new flame, a new fire inside of them—and they shake off all the old and all the compromise they've been living in.

01:09:26.466 --> 01:09:34.630
Maybe there's somebody on the other side of that camera right now who may not know Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

01:09:34.631 --> 01:09:41.678
I'm praying for you. Say this prayer after me: 'Lord Jesus, come into my heart.

01:09:41.679 --> 01:09:47.441
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life. Forgive me of my sins.

01:09:47.443 --> 01:09:55.698
Cleanse me from all unrighteousness. I turn away from the devil and all his evil works.

01:09:55.699 --> 01:10:04.603
I come to You, Jesus, as a vessel that is broken and needs You.

01:10:04.604 --> 01:10:11.981
Fill me with Your Holy Spirit. Cleanse me from all this sin. Thank You, Lord.

01:10:11.982 --> 01:10:17.999
I make You my Lord and Savior.'Make Him your Lord and Savior.

01:10:18.000 --> 01:10:26.633
I believe today, if you believe that in your heart and you confess Jesus as your Lord and Savior, you're going to be saved.

01:10:26.634 --> 01:10:32.442
If you just said that prayer and you believe it in your heart, find a church to go to.

01:10:32.443 --> 01:10:39.473
Find a place to go to and get in the word. Get your Bible. Download the Bible app on your phone.

01:10:39.474 --> 01:10:47.999
If you have an iPhone or an Android phone, download the Bible on your phone and read it every day. Let that word become real to you.

01:10:48.000 --> 01:10:55.123
Get it inside of you, and Jesus will change you from the top of your head to the soles of your feet.

01:10:55.124 --> 01:11:00.070
I just want to tell you again: Jesus loves you and Jesus cares.

01:11:00.071 --> 01:11:10.479
Find a good Bible-based church; if you have to, find one online that will teach you the word of God and help you in your Christian walk.

01:11:10.480 --> 01:11:14.686
There are a lot of good churches out there; find them. If you're not in that area, watch them online.

01:11:14.687 --> 01:11:23.867
Build your faith up and it'll change you. All right, thank you for watching, and hopefully this meant something to you.

01:11:23.868 --> 01:11:38.496
If you don't agree with any of it, put it in the trash. If it blessed you, share it with somebody. Thank you and God bless you all. Bye-bye.

